  "description": "<p>根据全球卫生组织发布的最新报告中称蓝藻将会威胁人类和生活在河水里动物，当人类在含有蓝藻的河水中游泳可能会感染一种叫做蓝藻毒素的病菌，导致皮肤过 敏、 胃痉挛、呕吐、肌肉关节疼痛和肝损害等严重危害，严重者甚至可能会危及生命。为此都来自的VTT科学研究中心的科学家研制除了一种便携式的检测设备，方便 普通消费者及时对当前水质进行检测。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2df33c1d/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242866.htm&amp;t=VTT%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%AE%A4%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%E8%93%9D%E8%97%BB%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%BF%E6%90%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242866.htm&amp;t=VTT%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%AE%A4%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%E8%93%9D%E8%97%BB%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%BF%E6%90%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242866.htm&amp;t=VTT%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%AE%A4%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%E8%93%9D%E8%97%BB%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%BF%E6%90%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242866.htm&amp;t=VTT%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%AE%A4%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%E8%93%9D%E8%97%BB%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%BF%E6%90%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a hr